{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tutorial-js","path":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Vector/SmoothMeth/","webpackCompilationHash":"b56fc1f276773fcd7503","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>当前 SuperMap UGC(Universal GIS Class)系列产品中针对线、面数据集提供的光滑处理方法主要有B样条法和磨角法两种方法。</p>\n<h3 id=\"一、使用-b-样条法进行光滑处理\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-b-%E6%A0%B7%E6%9D%A1%E6%B3%95%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%89%E6%BB%91%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>一、使用 <strong>B 样条法进行光滑处理</strong></h3>\n<p>光滑系数是控制光滑度的参数， 在 B 样条法中也可以理解成线段上两个节点之间插入点后分隔的段数。</p>\n<p>对非闭合线段进行光滑处理时要尽量保持原来曲线的形状，为了实现此目标通常采用的方法是：首、末两端点位置保持不变，增加首、末两端线段插入点后分段的数目（通常是光滑系数的二倍）。</p>\n<p>设置光滑系数，取大于等于 2 的值有效，该值越大，线对象或面对象边界的节点数越多，也就越光滑。建议取值范围为[2,10]。</p>\n<p>B 样条法插点数目计算方式分为闭合线和非闭合线两种：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果线段闭合，最终节点数目=(控制点数目-1)*光滑系数+1</li>\n<li>如果线段非闭合，最终节点数目=（控制点数目+1）*光滑系数+1</li>\n<li>\n<p>控制点可以理解为光滑前线对象上实际的节点数目。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>下面所示的是闭合线进行光滑时候的插入点情况。（注意闭合曲线的实际点数比显示的少一个，因为在第一个点与最后一个点的位置是重合的）</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>对闭合线进行光滑处理时光滑系数设置为 2，即每段之间插入 1 个点使其分隔成 2 段从而实现光滑。</p>\n<p>光滑前4个点，光滑后7个点。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4a33af77df0f0dadd04b996e7e66cffe/b70fd/BLine1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 471px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 40.552016985138%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"BLine1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4a33af77df0f0dadd04b996e7e66cffe/b70fd/BLine1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4a33af77df0f0dadd04b996e7e66cffe/6a467/BLine1.png 210w,\n/static/4a33af77df0f0dadd04b996e7e66cffe/635b1/BLine1.png 420w,\n/static/4a33af77df0f0dadd04b996e7e66cffe/b70fd/BLine1.png 471w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 471px) 100vw, 471px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>对闭合线进行光滑处理时光滑系数设置为 10，光滑效果如下。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bddc33b12f62743c2143ebbf6d404cf3/b70fd/BLine2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 471px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 40.552016985138%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"BLine2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/bddc33b12f62743c2143ebbf6d404cf3/b70fd/BLine2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bddc33b12f62743c2143ebbf6d404cf3/6a467/BLine2.png 210w,\n/static/bddc33b12f62743c2143ebbf6d404cf3/635b1/BLine2.png 420w,\n/static/bddc33b12f62743c2143ebbf6d404cf3/b70fd/BLine2.png 471w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 471px) 100vw, 471px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>下面所示的是非闭合线进行光滑时候的插入点情况。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>对非闭合线进行光滑处理时光滑系数设置为 2，即中间每段之间插入 1 个点使其分隔成 2 段从而实现光滑，首末两端段数分隔成 4 段（插入 3 个点）。</p>\n<p>光滑前6个点，光滑后15个点。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/da3c207b4fa8ac8f84f44be1f795fd49/b70fd/BLine3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 471px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 44.5859872611465%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"BLine3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/da3c207b4fa8ac8f84f44be1f795fd49/b70fd/BLine3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/da3c207b4fa8ac8f84f44be1f795fd49/6a467/BLine3.png 210w,\n/static/da3c207b4fa8ac8f84f44be1f795fd49/635b1/BLine3.png 420w,\n/static/da3c207b4fa8ac8f84f44be1f795fd49/b70fd/BLine3.png 471w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 471px) 100vw, 471px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>对非闭合线进行光滑处理时光滑系数设置为 10，光滑效果如下。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2bb1b5e9ef0991c44bd5374f27c98466/b70fd/BLine4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 471px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 44.5859872611465%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"BLine4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2bb1b5e9ef0991c44bd5374f27c98466/b70fd/BLine4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2bb1b5e9ef0991c44bd5374f27c98466/6a467/BLine4.png 210w,\n/static/2bb1b5e9ef0991c44bd5374f27c98466/635b1/BLine4.png 420w,\n/static/2bb1b5e9ef0991c44bd5374f27c98466/b70fd/BLine4.png 471w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 471px) 100vw, 471px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h3 id=\"二、磨角法进行光滑处理\"><a href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E7%A3%A8%E8%A7%92%E6%B3%95%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%89%E6%BB%91%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>二、磨角法进行光滑处理</h3>\n<p>磨角法是一种运算相对简单，处理速度比较快的光滑方法，但是效果比较局限。它的运算过程主要是先对两节点之间的线段插入两个点，即三等分原有线段，然后原有节点两边相邻的插入点进行连线，从而抹去原有几何对象中节点所在的角，完成一次以上过程为一次磨角过程。</p>\n<p>其中光滑系数指的是磨角的次数，光滑系数值越高，获得结果对象中插入点也越多，结果也就越接近光滑。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>下面是用磨角法对封闭四边形进行光滑处理的过程，光滑系数是 2 即进行两次磨角处理。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dd54d6092e4eceb6db514d617e25b122/b70fd/Polish.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 471px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 89.171974522293%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Polish\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/dd54d6092e4eceb6db514d617e25b122/b70fd/Polish.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dd54d6092e4eceb6db514d617e25b122/6a467/Polish.png 210w,\n/static/dd54d6092e4eceb6db514d617e25b122/635b1/Polish.png 420w,\n/static/dd54d6092e4eceb6db514d617e25b122/b70fd/Polish.png 471w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 471px) 100vw, 471px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>非闭合线进行磨角光滑处理时中间线段和节点处理过程同上，首末两个端点保持位置不变。</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"光滑方法说明","next":null,"prev":null},"fields":{"path":"content\\tutorial\\DataProcessing\\Vector\\SmoothMeth.zh.md","slug":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Vector/SmoothMeth/","langKey":"zh"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Vector/SmoothMeth/"}}}